headline: IDEXX Laboratories Elects Karen Peacock to Board of Directors
summary: WESTBROOK, Maine, October 07, 2025--IDEXX Laboratories, Inc. (NASDAQ: IDXX), a global leader in pet healthcare innovation, today announced the election of Karen Peacock to the Company's Board of Directors, effective October 6, 2025.
